&lt;p&gt;
The VX2 for oil (fluid viscosity not exceeding 50 mm&#xb2;/s) is available with brass and stainless steel body. Three body sizes are available, with port size ranges from 1/8 to 1/2 inch. FKM seal is standard and EPDM is optional. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 0.23 to 2.21.
